marketingBullets:
Proud to offer you our 4.5-Star Rated Medicare Advantage plan

• $0 premium for medical and prescription drug coverage

• $0 co-pay for preventive care, including many health screenings

• $0 co-pay for a 90-day supply of Tier 1 and 2 drugs, with home delivery

• SilverSneakers® gym membership and fitness classes at no additional cost

• HouseCalls program for an annual in-home clinical visit at no additional cost

• $10 co-pay for primary care visits

• $50 co-pay for specialist visits

• Routine hearing exam and low co-pay for hearing aids

• Routine vision, plus a credit for glasses or contacts
